00059 void CDFFileReaderTest::ReadSmallCDFFileBasicTest()
00060 {
00061         CDFData data;
00062         CDFFileReader reader;
00063         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_NO_THROW(reader.SetFilename(SMALL_CDF_FILE));
00064         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_NO_THROW(reader.Read(data));
00065 
00066         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data.GetFilename() == SMALL_CDF_FILE);
00067 
00068         FileHeader* fh = data.GetFileHeader();
00069         u_int32_t pos = fh->GetFirstDataGroupFilePos();
00070         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(pos == 0x1BD);
00071         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data.GetProbeSetCnt() == 10);
00072         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data.GetArrayRows() == 10*2);
00073         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data.GetArrayCols() == 11);
00074 }

00154 void CDFFileReaderTest::CheckSmallCDFProbeSetInformation(int32_t index, CDFProbeSetInformation& psi)
00155 {
00156         // values expected in the file
00157         // u_int8_t unitType = 3;
00158         u_int32_t numGroups = 1;
00159         DirectionType direction = ProbeSenseDirection;
00160         u_int32_t numLists = 11;
00161         u_int8_t cellsPerList = 2;
00162         u_int32_t numCells = numLists*cellsPerList;
00163 
00164         wchar_t name[100];
00165         FormatString1(name, 100, L"biob_%d", index);
00166 
00167         // Check the CDFProbeSetInformation
00168         // TODO: do we need to add a method to get unitType from CDFProbeSetInformation.  It goes in but doesn't come out.
00169         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(psi.GetName() == name);
00170         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(direction == psi.GetDirection());
00171         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(numLists == psi.GetNumLists());
00172         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(numGroups == psi.GetNumGroups());
00173         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(numCells == psi.GetNumCells());
00174         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(cellsPerList == psi.GetNumCellsPerList());
00175         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(index == psi.GetProbeSetNumber());
00176 
00177         // Check the CDFProbeGroupInformation
00178         CDFProbeGroupInformation pgi;
00179         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_NO_THROW(psi.GetGroupInformation(0, pgi));
00180         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(pgi.GetName() == name);
00181         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(direction == pgi.GetDirection());
00182         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(numLists == pgi.GetNumLists());
00183         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(numCells == pgi.GetNumCells());
00184         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(cellsPerList == pgi.GetNumCellsPerList());
00185 
00186         // Check the CDFProbeInformation
00187         CDFProbeInformation pi;
00188         for (u_int32_t list = 0; list < numLists; ++list)
00189         {
00190                 u_int32_t startCell = list*cellsPerList;
00191                 for (u_int32_t cellInList = 0; cellInList < cellsPerList; ++cellInList)
00192                 {
00193                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_NO_THROW(pgi.GetCell(startCell+cellInList, pi));
00194                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(pi.GetX() == list);
00195                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(pi.GetY() == index*cellsPerList+cellInList);
00196                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(pi.GetListIndex() == list);
00197                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(pi.GetExpos() == list);
00198                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(pi.GetPBase() == 'C');
00199                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(pi.GetTBase() == 'G');
00200                 }
00201         }
00202 }

00299 void CDFFileReaderTest::CheckSmallQCCDFProbeSetInformation(int32_t index, CDFQCProbeSetInformation& psi)
00300 {
00301         // values expected in the file
00302         //u_int32_t numGroups = 1;
00303         u_int32_t numLists = 11;
00304         u_int8_t cellsPerList = 2;
00305         u_int32_t numCells = numLists*cellsPerList;
00306 
00307         wchar_t qcType[100];
00308         FormatString1(qcType, 100, L"control_%d", index);
00309 
00310         // Check the CDFQCProbeSetInformation
00311         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(psi.GetQCProbeSetType() == qcType);
00312         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(numCells == psi.GetNumCells());
00313 
00314         // Check the CDFQCProbeInformation
00315         CDFQCProbeInformation pi;
00316         for (u_int32_t list = 0; list < numLists; ++list)
00317         {
00318                 u_int32_t startCell = list*cellsPerList;
00319                 for (u_int32_t cellInList = 0; cellInList < cellsPerList; ++cellInList)
00320                 {
00321                         bool expectedPM = (cellInList % 2)? true : false;
00322                         bool expectedBG = (list % 2) ? true : false;
00323 
00324                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_NO_THROW(psi.GetProbeInformation(startCell+cellInList, pi));
00325                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(pi.GetX() == list);
00326                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(pi.GetY() == index*cellsPerList+cellInList);
00327                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(pi.GetPLen() == 25);
00328                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(pi.IsPerfectMatchProbe() == expectedPM);
00329                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(pi.IsBackgroundProbe() == expectedBG);
00330                 }
00331         }
00332 }
